       FILE-CONTROL.

           COPY "SELFUNCIONARIO.cob".

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.

           COPY "FDFUNCIONARIO.cob".

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-BEGIN.
